column5: Well, I had a wonderful day today. Went out to Anse aux sables and met up with Mike the Pike, his son Ryan, Marc Thorpe and his son Marc-Olivier. Caught a whack of perch and another fish that I'll let someone else talk about. I have some pics and even an entry for team #10. Just a great day. I can't do the report right now cause when I got home, I noticed that Helene had invited 6 friends and J has invited 3 of her friends who should arrive any minute. I'll post as soon as I can....maybe Mike will post something in the meantime. I'll be here later tonight I spose. Thanks for the great day, guys.
Yes I also had a great day with Marc,Roy and the two young lads Marc-Olivier and my boy Ryan.I am working on the report with pics.Coming soon.MTP
Nice one Roy.  Team #10 is by far the best squad.
I can't post because wimmins are in the house???... how wimpy is that???
Waits with baited breath, tap, tap, tap!!!!!  Glad to hear you guys had a good time and caught fish to boot  Joey
